ygData.messageBody:
Paineel is on the eq map, on the southern end of odus. the area looks like
a blasted ruin, the result of a magical war. Paineel is supposed to be
inside of a crater, so it may be quite large- perhaps they want to keep it
as something for the higher end graphics cards.
